citeinfo.title: Marcellus Gas Well Water Sources View

descript.abstract: This data set contains all approved water sources within water managment plans (WMP). A WMP contains water sources utilized in the fracture stimulation of Marcellus Shale natural gas wells in Pennsylvania.
descript.purpose: Dataset developed to serve the needs of DEP and is intended for educational purposes. The dataset will be continually updated on an as needed basis.
